msgid ""
"Use Ray Data readers and Dataset operations from Klein for Ray without "
"duplicating the installed Ray API."
msgstr "在 Klein for Ray 中使用 Ray Data reader 和 Dataset 操作，而不重复定义已安装的 Ray API。"

msgid "Ray Data interoperability"
msgstr "Ray Data 互操作"

msgid ""
"For a connector-oriented summary of readers, transforms, writers, "
"execution modes, and guarantees, see the dedicated [Ray Data "
"connector](connectors/ray-data.md)."
msgstr ""
"有关 reader、转换、writer、执行模式和保证的连接器概览，请参阅专门的 [Ray Data 连接器](connectors/ray-"
"data.md)。"

msgid ""
"Klein for Ray does not copy Ray Data's loading APIs. Those signatures "
"change between Ray releases and duplicating them creates an immediately "
"stale second API. Instead, source factories are exposed directly from "
"`ray.klein`:"
msgstr ""
"Klein for Ray 不复制 Ray Data 的加载 API。这些签名会随 Ray 版本变化，复制它们会立即形成过时的第二套 "
"API。数据源工厂会直接从 `ray.klein` 公开："

msgid ""
"`ray.klein.read_csv`, `read_parquet`, `range`, and other factories "
"resolve their installed `ray.data` counterpart dynamically."
msgstr "`ray.klein.read_csv`、`read_parquet`、`range` 等工厂会动态解析到已安装的 `ray.data` 对应项。"

msgid "`stream.data` resolves public `ray.data.Dataset` methods."
msgstr "`stream.data` 会解析公共的 `ray.data.Dataset` 方法。"

msgid ""
"Resolution happens against the installed Ray version when the graph "
"executes. Arguments are forwarded unchanged, while `help()`, "
"`inspect.signature()`, and the docstring come from that same Ray "
"installation."
msgstr ""
"图执行时会针对已安装的 Ray 版本进行解析。参数保持原样转发，而 `help()`、`inspect.signature()` "
"和文档字符串均来自同一 Ray 安装。"

msgid ""
"New Ray factories and Dataset methods are available automatically. "
"Inspect the current installation with `dir(ray.klein)` and "
"`stream.data.available`."
msgstr ""
"新的 Ray factory 和 Dataset 方法会自动可用。可通过 `dir(ray.klein)` 和 "
"`stream.data.available` 查看当前安装。"

msgid "Ray Data expressions"
msgstr "Ray Data 表达式"

msgid ""
"Klein forwards Ray 2.56 expression objects unchanged, so their exact AST,"
" schema inference, optimizer rules, and execution operators remain owned "
"by Ray Data in batch mode. The expression-bearing `with_column` and "
"`filter(expr=...)` forms also have native Klein streaming "
"implementations:"
msgstr ""
"Klein 会原样转发 Ray 2.56 表达式对象，因此在批处理模式下，其确切 AST、模式推断、优化器规则和执行算子仍由 Ray Data "
"负责。包含表达式的 `with_column` 和 `filter(expr=...)` 形式也有原生 Klein 流处理实现："

msgid ""
"This includes Ray 2.56's column/literal AST, arithmetic, comparison, "
"boolean, null and membership operators, aliases, PyArrow and Python UDF "
"expressions, string/list/array/map/struct/datetime namespaces, synthetic "
"IDs/random/UUIDs, and the dedicated `download()` expression. In batch "
"mode, `download()` is not converted to a row UDF: `Dataset.with_column()`"
" retains Ray's URI partitioning and concurrent download plan. In "
"streaming mode, Klein evaluates one URI per record in a bounded, order-"
"preserving asynchronous window. A null or unreadable URI produces `None`,"
" matching Ray 2.56's download operator."
msgstr ""
"这包括 Ray 2.56 的列/字面量 AST、算术、比较、布尔、空值和成员运算符、别名、PyArrow 与 Python UDF "
"表达式、字符串/列表/数组/映射/结构体/日期时间命名空间、合成 ID/随机数/UUID，以及专用的 `download()` "
"表达式。在批处理模式下，`download()` 不会转换成逐行 UDF：`Dataset.with_column()` 会保留 Ray 的 "
"URI 分区和并发下载计划。在流处理模式下，Klein 会在有界且保序的异步窗口中逐条计算 URI。空 URI 或不可读 URI 会生成 "
"`None`，与 Ray 2.56 的下载算子一致。"

msgid "Choose Klein or Ray Data operations"
msgstr "选择 Klein 或 Ray Data 操作"

msgid ""
"Use native Klein methods such as `stream.map` and `stream.filter` for "
"general unbounded transformations. `stream.data.with_column(name, expr)` "
"and `stream.data.filter(expr=expr)` work in both modes; other "
"`stream.data` transforms and all terminal consumers remain batch-only."
msgstr ""
"一般无界转换请使用 `stream.map` 和 `stream.filter` 等原生 Klein "
"方法。`stream.data.with_column(name, expr)` 和 "
"`stream.data.filter(expr=expr)` 可在两种模式下工作；其他 `stream.data` "
"转换和所有终端消费操作仅支持批处理。"

msgid ""
"`ray.klein.read_kafka(..., trigger=\"once\")` delegates to Ray Data, "
"while `trigger=\"continuous\"` selects Klein's unbounded, checkpoint-"
"aware source. The continuous source keeps the same raw record schema and "
"modern Confluent `consumer_config` style, adds source `concurrency`, "
"partition discovery, and poll-batch controls, and runs only on the "
"streaming backend. Put Confluent authentication settings in "
"`consumer_config`."
msgstr ""
"`ray.klein.read_kafka(..., trigger=\"once\")` 委托给 Ray Data，而 "
"`trigger=\"continuous\"` 选择 Klein 的无界、检查点感知数据源。连续数据源保留相同的原始记录模式和现代 "
"Confluent `consumer_config` 风格，增加数据源 "
"`concurrency`、分区发现和轮询批次控制，并且只在流处理后端运行。请将 Confluent 认证设置放在 "
"`consumer_config` 中。"

msgid ""
"This explicit boundary also resolves name collisions. For example, "
"`stream.map(fn)` is Klein's stream/batch operation, while "
"`stream.data.map(fn)` is the currently installed Ray Dataset method."
msgstr ""
"这条明确边界也解决了名称冲突。例如，`stream.map(fn)` 是 Klein 的流/批操作，而 `stream.data.map(fn)`"
" 是当前已安装的 Ray Dataset 方法。"

msgid "Arbitrary and third-party operations"
msgstr "任意操作和第三方操作"

msgid ""
"The named dynamic methods cover every public Dataset factory and method. "
"The explicit forms cover third-party connectors and multi-step Ray "
"objects such as `GroupedData` without requiring Klein to understand those"
" types:"
msgstr ""
"具名动态方法覆盖每个公共 Dataset 工厂和方法。显式形式可覆盖第三方连接器，以及 `GroupedData` 等多步骤 Ray 对象，无需 "
"Klein 理解这些类型："

msgid ""
"A transform callable must return exactly one `Dataset`. A consumer may "
"return any value. Consumers remain lazy: the terminal call registers the "
"consumer and `ray.klein.execute(\"job-name\").get()` returns its result."
msgstr ""
"转换可调用对象必须恰好返回一个 `Dataset`。消费者可以返回任意值。消费者仍是惰性的：终结调用会注册该消费者，"
"`ray.klein.execute(\"job-name\").get()` 返回其结果。"

msgid ""
"Other Klein streams passed anywhere inside positional or keyword "
"arguments are automatically compiled into Dataset dependencies. This "
"supports methods such as `union`, `zip`, and `join` without exposing "
"compiler internals:"
msgstr ""
"在位置参数或关键字参数任意位置传入的其他 Klein stream 都会自动编译为 Dataset 依赖项。这可支持 `union`、`zip` "
"和 `join` 等方法，而无需暴露编译器内部实现："

msgid "Advanced: isolate graph-building contexts"
msgstr "高级用法：隔离图构建上下文"

msgid ""
"`KleinContext` can isolate multiple graph builders in one process. Its "
"`context.data` namespace remains available for explicitly scoped graph "
"builders, while ordinary application code should prefer the module-level "
"readers. Ray Data methods are generally unavailable directly on "
"`KleinContext` or `DataStream`; use `context.data.read_csv(...)` and "
"`stream.data.random_shuffle(...)` when the explicit namespace is needed. "
"The documented stable sink entry points are exceptions, including "
"`stream.write_sql(...)`, which uses Ray Data in batch mode and Klein's "
"at-least-once DB-API sink in streaming mode."
msgstr ""
"`KleinContext` 可以在一个进程中隔离多个图构建器。其 `context.data` "
"命名空间仍可用于显式限定作用域的图构建器，而普通应用代码应优先使用模块级 reader。通常不能直接在 `KleinContext` 或 "
"`DataStream` 上使用 Ray Data 方法；需要显式命名空间时，请使用 `context.data.read_csv(...)` 和"
" `stream.data.random_shuffle(...)`。文档中稳定的 Sink 入口点属于例外，包括 "
"`stream.write_sql(...)`：它在批处理模式下使用 Ray Data，在流处理模式下使用 Klein 的至少一次 DB-API "
"Sink。"
